body.codeblock:
@page :right{
    @bottom-center {
        content: "© 2017 - My Company Ltd \A All rights reserved";
        font-size: 0.5em;
        color: silver;
    }    
}

body.note:
Other page rules (such as the table-of-contents) override the contents of the
        @bottom-center because they are more specific. If you need to also print
      the copyright in the TOC pages, then use this as the
      selector:@page :right, table-of-contents:right {
  ...
}
